# textdomain: mcl_panes
Glass panes are thin layers of glass which neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them.=Los paneles de vidrio son capas delgadas de vidrio que se conectan perfectamente a otros paneles de vidrio a medida que los colocas.
Stained glass panes are thin layers of stained glass which neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them. They come in many different colors.=Los paneles de vidrio son capas delgadas de vidrio que se conectan perfectamente a otros vidiros a medida que los colocas. Vienen en muchos colores diferentes.
Stained Glass Pane=Panel de vidrio tintado
Iron Bars=Barrotes de hierro
Iron bars neatly connect to their neighbors as you build them.=Los barrotes de hierro se conectan perfectamente a sus vecinos a medida que los construyes.
Glass Pane=Panel de vidrio
@1 Glass Pane=Panel de vidrio teñido de @1
